Default `Effect.all` is short-circuit: the first failing effect interrupts its siblings and the error channel is a single `E`. With `mode: "validate"`, every effect runs to completion and the error channel becomes a record/tuple of `Option<E>` at the same shape as the inputs, so you can see every failure at once.

